    Find out what happens after you click send.

    Send a tracked email
    1. Compose an email.
    2. Make sure the "Track" checkbox is checked.
    3. Send the email and receive a notification when your recipient opens it!

    Send a tracked email

    Use a template
    1. Click the Gmail Compose button.
    2. Click the "Templates" button.
    3. Choose a template from your template library.
    4. Send the email.
    Use a template
    Set a reminder
    1. Compose an email.
    2. Click on the "Remind" button.
    3. Select a date and time.
    4. Click "Set" to finish.
    5. Send the email and get the scheduled reminder.
    Set a reminder
    Schedule an email to send later
    1. Compose an email.
    2. Click "Later" beside the send button.
    3. Select a date, time, and time zone.
    4. Click "Confirm" to schedule the email.
    Schedule an email
